thread.title: Michael

author: Michael
title: Michael
text: Two weeks before the Bruce Springsteen concert in Melbourne, I assumed we had no chances of picking up a ticket. Through Ticketmaster Resale, we managed to get two seats on the floor, three rows from the front, at no more than face value. They were delivered electronically, as promised. The Ticketmaster service was excellent. Bruce Springsteen was phenomenal!
